  "texts": [
    "All completed the survey.",
    "Their demographics are shown in ►Table 1.",
    "Heat maps of the ratings for clinical, research, and education tasks are shown in ►Tables 2-4.",
    "Of the 23 tasks, 16 (69.6%) had positive ratings by at least half of the participants.",
    "The highest rated tasks were \"assist with vaccine development by predicting the antigenicity of different proteins from genomic data\" (25 positive ratings from 30 participants), \"model the spread and transmission of an infectious disease\" (25 positive ratings), \"generate case studies for training purposes\" (24 positive ratings), \"monitor data for an emerging disease cluster\" (24 positive ratings), and \"generate alerts to improve compliance with clinical guidelines\" (24 positive ratings)."
